{"tid":767880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"忽發奇想，可唔可以遊說尖咀果班商戶申請禁制令趕走班大媽？","createTime":"2018-08-05T02:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T03:04:06.000Z","uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2f3ef91d867c3d0d48552b78a39a28f29c06f970","tid":767880,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T02:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n禁制令(Injunction)是指由法庭判令要求某人或團體強制履行或停止某種行動，屬衡平法的一種補救方式，通過回復原來狀況來保障受害人的權益。禁制令分為臨時和永久性，法庭會就被告對原告人作出的惡意滋擾、誹謗、侵權、侵犯私隱等不當行為頒布禁制；被禁制者如無法遵從，將會面臨民事或刑事上的處罰。"},{"pid":"0054fba58c47fd687d92133b774bad92381dd875","tid":767880,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T02:37:42.000Z","msg":"係佢地門口唱就會理下你既"},{"pid":"6d647a8ba1f9424d64aefb6b1207d5e3a36e7faa","tid":767880,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T02:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6773a07a7b52ddfdd80c233982656fb47e5c2d","tid":767880,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:01:55.000Z","msg":"就算唔申請 都可以告遊蕩非法集會<br />\n官字兩個口嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff803e6f4801f8cf6d920299a7041faf00eaa58","tid":767880,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:03:33.000Z","msg":"禁制令重要告指定人<br />\n你想告曬全部人？"},{"pid":"5b3620fca75e9bce578ee5f05434c37a453d09e1","tid":767880,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:04:06.000Z","msg":"香港警察唔會將香港法例套用係蝗身上"}]}